 converged for \\St$=0.2$. Furthermore,\nwe report that our numerical simulations significantly dissipate turbulent\nkinetic energy on scales less than 6-8 grid points.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Sep 2022 17:45:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
