al Method, Network Design, $f$-Connectivity Problem,\nNear-Minimum Cuts, Approximation Algorithms, Flexible Graph Connectivity. }\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Sep 2022 17:47:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 18:51:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
