imentally verified on the Copernicus mobile robot. We further extend it\nto the bicycle model and demonstrate collision avoidance under various\nscenarios in the CARLA simulator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 11:09:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 11:13:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2023 05:29:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
