titatively analyzed in this study\noffer microscopic understanding to the origin of the solvent quality dependent\nosmotic pressure of 2D polymer solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 12:07:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-26"}
