duce the completion time for\n3000 functions by up to 61% compared to a randomized algorithm and the\nin-memory data store can speed up data transfers by up to 3x compared to a\nshared file system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 14:56:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
